<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idd2071fe7-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to section 519 of the former Appendix to this title prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idd2071fe8-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idd2071fe9-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section applicable to any case not final before <date date="2003-12-19">Dec. 19, 2003</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/108/189/s3">section 3 of Pub. L. 108–189</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t50/s3901">section 3901 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
